node.text:
Maintaining a healthy routine is a huge part of getting prepared to film - I have to be in great shape to compete, so working out and eating well are super important 💪🏼 After I've gotten all sweaty from working out, I love to give my face a deep and gentle cleanse and do a firming massage with a serum to keep it hydrated & glowing. 
What is your healthy routine? Tell me below ⬇️⬇️
-- Shop the brush (link in stories), my #LUNA3 by @foreo on @sephora
#ad #workinonmyfitness #thechallenge #healthylifestyle #fitnesslife

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jenna Compono on August 17, 2021 tagging @sephora, @ediblebeautyau, and @brittanybrockiephotography. May be an image of 1 person and bottle.

node.text: I’ve talked about my struggles with melasma and I’ve found my new favorite skincare products that I can’t live without during pregnancy from @ediblebeautyau ❤ All of their skincare is natural, vegan and pregnancy safe! The products I have been using help with hyperpigmentation and melasma & are available online at @sephora #cleanatsephora

node.text: The last wedding we went to before the baby comes at 38 weeks pregnant! I think I’ve been to 20 weddings since I’ve been pregnant, and wore heels every time. I think it’s safe to say I will not be wearing heels anymore until WAY AFTER the baby is born 😅
